headline: Think It's Too Late to Buy Axon Enterprise Stock? Here's Why There's Still Time.
summary: Axon Enterprise (NASDAQ: AXON) is one of the best-performing stocks of the last 10 years, up roughly 2,000% during that time.  The maker of the TASER electrical weapon and body cameras has delivered consistent growth and technological innovation.  A strong software business complement its hardware as well.
